== Configuration details ==

A partially completed kernel config for this model, based on [//forums.gentoo.org/viewtopic-t-1051430.html Pappy's preconfigs] can be found [//bitbucket.org/experimentfailed/gentoo-kernel-configs here]. It has been tested to get a system booting and running a base install of Xorg with no additional configuration.

There is also a forum thread [//forums.gentoo.org/viewtopic-t-1066726.html here].

